Class Task

java.lang.Object
ntnu.idatt1002.model.Task
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Task
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
The class Task represents a task. This class provides access methods for all fields contained within. The class also provides hashCode and a equals method as well as a toString method.
